<br>
That's what I did and after a couple arena raids (about 4-5 hours max) and I was max ally.  Also look out for guilds doing statue or vindi.  Faction on the temple mobs is huge. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ushelseadruid.showPublicProfile?language=EN>ShelseaDruid</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://members.home.com/sigs/shelsea.jpg" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/5/02 3:11:02 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4639.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: How to get Coldain Faction</span><hr size=1> Easier yet - go to the Luclin Spires and kill Draekkel Dire Wolves...<br>
<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ubloatboy.showPublicProfile?language=EN>bloatboy</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/5/02 3:40:26 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4639.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: How to get Coldain Faction</span><hr size=1> GD giant fort area has a few higher level giants that give good faction. In a few hours of hunting there I went from apprehensive to kindly, so going from max KoS to Ally might take some time.<br>
Still the fort/spires area gets a lot of giants/dogs and seems to give the best Coldain faction I've seen yet.<br>
Arena is Kael is no good because most of the mobs there don't give Coldain faction <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :( --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/frown.gif ALT=":("><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uteyrbackblader.showPublicProfile?language=EN>TeyrBackblader</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/5/02 5:15:29 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4639.topic&index=8>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: How to get Coldain Faction</span><hr size=1> Go to GD near the giant fort, kill giant upon giant upon giant...collect heads and toes...turn in toes (4x at a time) for first shawl, get the box, turn in heads (10x combined in box) for second shawl...destroy shawl and repeat...by the time you collected enuf heads to do this one like 3 times...you should be ally. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/bthesafehouse.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=roketr>Roketr</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/5/02 11:04:49 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4639.topic&index=9>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: How to get Coldain Faction</span><hr size=1> Or you could just hangout when someone kills Tormax and shoot him once with a bow.<br>
<br>
Do that 3-4 times youll be ally coldain. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/umikar.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Mikar</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/6/02 4:10:16 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4639.topic&index=10>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: How to get Coldain Faction</span><hr size=1> Tormax doesnt give Coldain faction - only Dain and Yelinak. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/upraetorthecrusader.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Praetor the Crusader</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/6/02 10:09:29 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4639.topic&index=11>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: How to get Coldain Faction</span><hr size=1> The 9th ring quest cycle at Iceshard Manor in Kael.  I went from max kos to ally in about a day and a half around that area. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><br><font color=#FF0000>- </font><a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/bthesafehouse>The Safehouse</a><font color=#FF0000> - </font><a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13>Quests of Norrath</a> <font color=#FF0000> - </font><a href="http://www.thesafehouse.org">The Safehouse website</a><font color=#FF0000> - </font> <center><a href="http://www.guildboss.com"><img
